  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="column last span-20 prepend-2">
	<div class="column span-10"><h1>recortr<span>beta</span></h1></div>
	<div class="column span-10 last" style="text-align: right;"><h1 style="color: #999999; font-weight: normal;">clipcropcut</h1></div>
      </div>
      <div class="column last span-20 prepend-2" id="form-container">
	<form action="/" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" target="upload_iframe">
	  <fieldset>
	    <label for="mp3_upload">Upload your MP3 and be ready for the awesomeness:</label>
	    <input type="file" id="mp3_upload" name="mp3_upload" />
	    <img src="/images/ajax-loader.gif" id="ajax-loader" />
	  </fieldset>
	</form>
      </div>
      <iframe name="upload_iframe" id="upload_iframe" src="" style="display:none;"></iframe>
      <div class="column last span-20 prepend-2" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
	<div id="waveform">
	  <div id="waveform-selection">
	    <div id="waveform-load-progress">
	    </div>
	    <div id="waveform-play-progress">
	    </div>
	    <button>
	      <img src="/images/thumb_icon_play_rot_0.png" />
	    </button>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div class="column last" id="download-link">
	  <a href="">Download the clip</a>
	</div>
      </div>
      <div class="column last span-20 prepend-2" id="about">
	<p><span>recortr</span> is an online tool for making clips out of your MP3s. It is an experiment and an excuse to play with <a href="http://sinatra.rubyforge.org/">Sinatra web framework</a>, <a href="http://jquery.com">jQuery</a>, <a href="http://www.blueprintcss.org/">Blueprint</a>, <a href="http://www.schillmania.com/projects/soundmanager2/">soundmanager2</a> and <a href="http://www.cairographics.org/">Cairo</a>. <span>recortr</span> was written by <a href="http://jazzido.com">Manuel Aristar√°n</a>.</p>
	<p>It's been tested on Firefox 3 and Safari on a Mac.</p>
      </div>
